data.description: Seller is offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs and pre-paids.In the heart of Karns. This beautiful three-bedroom Villa is looking for a new owner! Three spacious bedrooms with the primary bedroom on the main level, along with laundry room on the main level , all for the convenience of today's buyers.  This charmer comes with all the bells and whistles: granite counter tops, under cabinet lighting in the kitchen, upgraded lighting fixtures and a fenced in back yard .  Hurry, your future home awaits! :)
